  <title>Solutions – Break the Cycle</title>
</head>
<body>

  <%- include("partials/solutions_header") %>

  <main>
    <section class="intro">
      <h1>Our Solutions</h1>
      <p>We believe problems like cyber addiction, plagiarism, and academic underperformance can be solved through practical steps and community support. Here’s how we plan to break the cycle.</p>
    </section>

    <section class="Solutions">
      <article>
        <h2>Healthy Digital Habits</h2>
        <p>Tools: time-management apps, digital detox challenges.</p>
        <p>Actions: awareness campaigns, “no phones in class” pledges, positive alternatives (coding club, debate, arts).</p>
      </article>

      <article>
        <h2>Academic Integrity</h2>
        <p>Actions: plagiarism-prevention workshops, peer mentoring, honor code pledges.</p>
        <p>Tools: training on proper research and citation, teacher support for assessment changes.</p>
      </article>

      <article>
        <h2>Boosting Student Performance</h2>
        <p>Actions: study skills workshops, peer mentoring, motivational talks.</p>
        <p>Tools: Youth-Led Centre, tutoring programs, one-on-one check-ins.</p>
      </article>
    </section>

    <section class="Sustainability">
      <h1>Sustainability</h1>
      <ul>
        <li>Healthy habits → SDG 3 (Good Health & Well-Being), SDG 4 (Quality Education).</li>
        <li>Academic integrity → SDG 4 (Quality Education), SDG 16 (Peace, Justice & Strong Institutions).</li>
        <li>Student performance → SDG 4 (Quality Education), SDG 8 (Decent Work & Economic Growth).</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section class="transition">
      <h3>Click the button to enter the contact page</h3>
      <button onclick="location.href='/contact'">Contact</button>
    </section>
  </main>

  <%- include("partials/footer") %>

</body>
</html>